  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244415.htm", 
  "description": "<p>周四微软宣布了外界期待已久的重组计划，将现有的8个产品部门打散后组建成4个新部门，并对公司高管团队的每一位成员的职责进行了调整。当外界和9万多名 员工的工作时候鲍尔默在西雅图时报采访中表示：<strong>“我们从来没有裁员的计划，我们现在所做的重组是为了扩展公司”这就意味着未来微软将会雇佣更多的员工。</strong>根 据5月份的相关报道中指出微软计划雇佣数千员工来对WP系统和在中国的的云平台进行扩展。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e8bddea/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244415.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%EF%BC%9A%E9%87%8D%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%A3%81%E5%91%98+%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E4%BC%9A%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244415.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%EF%BC%9A%E9%87%8D%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%A3%81%E5%91%98+%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E4%BC%9A%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244415.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%EF%BC%9A%E9%87%8D%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%A3%81%E5%91%98+%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E4%BC%9A%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244415.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%EF%BC%9A%E9%87%8D%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%A3%81%E5%91%98+%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E4%BC%9A%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\